    "jei.relocate.advanced_blocks_mover_jei_info": "Advanced Blocks Mover has 2 modes, drop mode and normal mode. Normal mode works exactly like standard Blocks Mover, drop mode moves block from back to front but drops it as item.",
    "jei.relocate.blocks_destroyer_jei_info": "Blocks Destroyer breaks blocks in front of it.",
    "jei.relocate.blocks_detector_jei_info": "Blocks Detector emits redstone signal when block in front of it is the same block as block in build-in GUI. You can lock it using State Changer to disable opening GUI.",
