    "jei.relocate.blocks_mover_jei_info": "Blocks Mover moves blocks from back to front.",
    "jei.relocate.blocks_placer_jei_info": "Blocks Placer places blocks in front of it from build-in GUI",
    "jei.relocate.copper_cogwheel_jei_info": "Crafting element for most of Relocate Blocks.",
    "jei.relocate.notifier_jei_info": "Notifier plays sound when right clicked on it or powered. Unlike Note Blocks, Notifier plays sound even if top side is covered and sound isn't changing depends on block under it!",
